SAILOR

SKILL PROFICIENCIES: Athletics, Perception
TOOL PROFICIENCIES: Navigator's tools, Vehicles (water)
EQUIPMENT: Belaying pin (club)
           50ft of silk rope
           Lucky charm or random trinket
           Set of common clothes 
           Belt pouch containing 10gp
           
FEATURE: SHIP'S PASSAGE
Secure free passage on sailing ship for yourself and companions (have to assist crew during voyage).

SUGGESTED CHARACTERISTICS

VARIANT SAILOR: PIRATE
Unsavory reputation. Bad reputation feature.

VARIANT FEATURE: BAD REPUTATION 
Replaces Ship's Passage. Everyone is afraid of you. 
